      Stakeholder: cities - 2023: 0.0 - Metric: distribution of co-benefits - Yes<br/>distribution
      of co-benefits - Cost type: accidents - Stakeholder: citizens - 2023: 0.4 -
      Metric: distribution of co-benefits - Majority attributed to healthcare given
      a large amount of the damages caused by traffic accidents is a cost that the
      healthcare system needs to bear. Some is also attributed to citizens (improved
      well-being, reduced sick days, longer life). We attribute costs related to police,
      ambulance, etc. is included in the healthcare costs. Costs of closing roads,
      etc. is not included<br/>distribution of co-benefits - Cost type: accidents
